The paper deals with social group activity planning, which involves social network analysis, optimization, and algorithm design. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks), followed by cs.SOC (Social and Behavioral Sciences), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
